{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1366109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "取消早八考勤", "timestamp": 1617170571, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366119, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关:研究生34号楼北面住户 希望能推迟热水", "timestamp": 1617170633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366123, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我关心的是为什么是紫操，那同学们去哪里锻炼？我想踢球啊😭", "timestamp": 1617170668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366129, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关，只是想在紫操踢球", "timestamp": 1617170690, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "12点到3点休息行不……", "timestamp": 1617170697, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关，只想翘课", "timestamp": 1617170713, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366149, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "主要问题是早8，你剥夺同学们一个小时睡觉时间就要想法补回来，排练施工早晨9点开始，第一节课也9点开始，让同学们多睡一会，热水延迟到12点结束，图书馆和教学楼跟着晚一个小时", "timestamp": 1617170777, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "热水图书馆延时都会进一步公布。但是这件事本身就离谱", "timestamp": 1617170860, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366171, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关 建议延迟热水到十二点", "timestamp": 1617170917, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366194, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "延迟热水！图书馆晚关门！最好晚上不断电（熄灯无所谓）！\n推迟早八上课不现实，改动太大了，涉及人员过多，反抗不了。\n但以上这些应该是比较好办的", "timestamp": 1617171066, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关\n建议减免阳光长跑次数2次【这个诉求很合理可行了吧】", "timestamp": 1617171092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 熄灯不断电 支持", "timestamp": 1617171142, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366203, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学校的打算是热水十二点，图书馆十一点", "timestamp": 1617171158, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366207, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "图书馆热水都延迟到12点，给紫荆宿舍发免费电开空调替代开窗。", "timestamp": 1617171175, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366223, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "最好8:30之前不要进行音量过大的施工", "timestamp": 1617171361, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366282, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "利益相关，紫八南面用户，我想到以下三个令我满意的解决方案：\n1.给所有噪音影响到的楼加装隔音玻璃\n2.为我们安排远离施工噪音的临时住所\n3.发补助，我自己找地方住\n不过清华什么时候考虑过学生舒不舒服？", "timestamp": 1617171820, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366310, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 我的想法是，先争取，合理诉求都争取不到更有底气骂💩", "timestamp": 1617172060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1367029, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "图书馆开到十一点！紫八难民不想回去听噪音！\n", "timestamp": 1617179212, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1367576, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "阳光长跑减次数+1！！而且多减几次吧将近一个月呢！本来紫操晚上就是跑步高峰期，就着噪音跑也太吐了", "timestamp": 1617183887, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1369143, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 想提合理诉求一般都不会有什么效果。比如你想开一扇窗，你要是跟人说开一扇窗，没人会答应，你要是说要把房子拆了，那多半人们就乐意了", "timestamp": 1617199117, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1369165, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 268282, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议要求按照噪音污染防治法，要求昼间低于六十分贝，夜间低于五十分贝", "timestamp": 1617199369, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 268282, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "开个洞统计下紫操旁边受影响同学的诉求。\n比如推迟热水、推迟图书馆结束时间等等（刚刚在洞里看到的），我们正常生活还需要的可能的补偿方法。毕竟学校也给了生权的反馈渠道，骂的同时最好也能团结起来争取合理的权益。\n\n\n利益相关：紫八南面住户", "timestamp": 1617170498, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617199369, "url": "", "vote": {}}}